#include <vector>
using namespace std;
inline int next_int() {
	int n = 0;
	char c = getchar_unlocked();
	while (!('0' <= c && c <= '9')) {
	c = getchar_unlocked();
	}
	while ('0' <= c && c <= '9') {
  n = n * 10 + c - '0';
  c = getchar_unlocked();
 }
 return n;
}
